  <a href="{% url 'terms_of_service' %}" style="color: #fff; margin: 0 10px;">Term of Service</a> |
  <a href="{% url 'privacy_policy' %}" style="color: #fff; margin: 0 10px;">Privacy Policy</a>
</p>
